The paper deals with wireless communication systems, specifically simultaneous wireless information and power transfer (SWIPT) in cell-free massive multiple-input multiple-output (MIMO) systems. This involves information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), control theory (cs.SY), multimedia (cs.MM), and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
